    "created_at": "2015-07-30T00:04:08Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-30T00:04:08Z",
    "body": "> 1) the tray icon is stretched instead of fitted like the previous version\n\nIt has been fixed in #2370.\n\n> 2) clicked event is emitted on tray even though ctx menu is also shown \n\nYes.  In the v0.30.1 previous version, the clicked event will be ignored when there is context menu in tray due to the limitation of implementation. In v0.30.1, we remove this limitation.\n"
  },
