    "created_at": "2015-07-30T01:27:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-30T01:27:34Z",
    "body": "> 2) clicked event is emitted on tray even though ctx menu is also shown - unlike the previous versions\n\nI'm :+1: on emitting the `clicked` event even when menu is shown, generally loosing the the limitation of the API always gives developers more powers, also it matches the behavior of the `right-clicked` event on Windows, which also emits the event while the menu is shown.\n"
  },
